readme:
Service Usage

The service sends details to eMedical when a MOC records an audit finding against an exam in HAP. This is for storage, analysis and subsequent action.

Notification of issues detected with health case assessments back by the MOC to eMedical.
Initiated in any case where an assessment issue is added in respect of a clinic that has been identified as being shared between eMedical and the back end system.

Service Behaviour

This is an asynchronis service where details of the Health Case issue are passed from eMedical to HAP.
